quran[9{c,v,t}:
40,50,"woh poucheen ge"" kya tumahray paas tumahray rasool bayyaynaat le kar nahi atay rahay thay ?"" woh kahin ge"" haan"" jahannum ke ahal car bolein ge :"" phir to tum hi dua karo, aur kafiroon ki dua akart hi jaane wali hai """
40,51,"yaqeen jano ke hum apne Rasolo-n aur imaan laane walon ki madad iss duniya ki zindagi mein bhi laziman karte hain, aur uss roz bhi karen ge jab gawah kharray hon ge ,"
40,52,jab zaalmon ko un ki moazrat kuch bhi faida nah day gi aur unn par laanat parre gi aur bad tareen thikana unn ke hissay mein aeye ga
40,53,aakhir dekh lau ke moose ki hum ne rahnumai ki aur bani Israel ko is kitaab ka waris bana diya
40,54,jo aqal o Danish rakhnay walon ke liye hadaayat o nasiyaat thi
40,55,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, sabr karo, Allah ka wada Bar haq hai, apne qasoor ki maffi chaho aur subah o shaam apne rab ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karte raho"
40,56,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log kisi sanad o Hujjat ke baghair jo unn ke paas aayi ho, Allah ki ayaat mein jhagrre kar rahay hain unn ke dilon mein kibar bhara howa hai, magar woh uss barayi ko pounchanay walay nahi hain jis ka woh ghamand rakhtay hain bas Allah ki panah maang lau, woh sab kuch daikhta aur santa hai"
40,57,"asmano aur zameen ka peda karna insanon ko peda karne ki bah nisbat yaqeenan ziyada bara kaam hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
40,58,aur yeh nahi ho sakta ke andha aur Beena yaksaa ho jaye aur imandaar o Saleh aur bad krrdar barabar therain magar tum log kam hi kuch samajte ho
